atlas.entity

Class ModelComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • atlas.entity.PageComponent
      • atlas.entity.ModelComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<PageComponent>

    @Entity
public class ModelComponent
extends PageComponent
implements Serializable
    Represents a 3D model in page content. This entity class is mapped to "MODELCOMPONENT" database table. In addition to mapped properties, common PageComponent properties are present.
    Author:
    Michal Smrha
    See Also:
    PageContent, PageComponent, Serialized Form

        public Integer getCompOrder()
        Description copied from class: PageComponent
        Gets compOrder, which is used for sorting components within a page. Typically compOrder is an index of this component (1 = top-most component; 2 = second from top etc.) However, it does not have to be an index and components are simlpy sorted by this value.
        Specified by:
